author: Al Jazeera
title: In Pictures: China's Wuhan lifts coronavirus lockdown
description: Streets in the city of 11 million people were clogged and long queues seen at the airport, train and bus stations.
content:
Wuhan, the Chinese city where the new coronavirus reported to have emerged from, has ended its more-than two-month lockdown.
